reviewText: I love this movie and I'm glad that I found it.  Movie works great, no major issues!  Thanks for everything.

I have no complaints. Ive been ordering movies that I cant find at the stores. So its a great choice for all of us that like independent and foreign films! I will buy all my movies from here from now on.

I am in love with Ana Claudia Talancon. And, she's great in this picture. Probably, this movie is one of her best that I have ever seen. She is charming, funny, witty, and has good chemistry with her co-star.
I think that this a well done movie. Some profanity and other things that, if your a parent, you might not want your children to see. I like the fact that this movie takes place in Mexico City.
